query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('common-table-expression',
'cookies',
'exception',
'javascript',
'jquery',
'llvm',
'localization',
'mysql',
'passwords',
'routes',
'settings',
'swift2',
'time-series',
'wpf-controls');
